stories.description:
File: scripts/player_data.gd

Read the full file before making changes.

Find lose_sanity() (around line 80 per research). It currently contains:
   var has_resistance: bool = SaveManager.has_implant("implant_sanity")
   var actual: int = max(0, amount - (10 if has_resistance else 0))

Replace those two lines with:
   var imp_san: int = SaveManager.get_implants().get("implant_sanity", 0)
   var actual: int = max(0, amount - (10 * imp_san))

This makes each purchase of implant_sanity reduce incoming sanity damage by 10 (stacking). The rest of the function body stays unchanged.
